    <item>
      <title>分析师库尔卡尼称，亚马逊的预测“略有偏差”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/amazon-forecast-is-a-small-miss-analyst-kulkarni-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Roth Capital Partners 互联网和资本市场高级分析师 Rohit Kulkarni 对亚马逊第一季度的预测做出了回应。他在“Bloomberg The Close”节目中发表了讲话。亚马逊预计本季度的营业收入为 140 亿美元至 180 亿美元，低于分析师预期的 182 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/amazon-forecast-is-a-small-miss-analyst-kulkarni-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:02:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
