      <title>Bessent 称房利美和房地美的释放取决于利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/bessent-says-fannie-freddie-release-depends-on-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特表示，是否解除房利美和房地美的托管将取决于抵押贷款利率的影响。贝森特在接受彭博社记者 Saleha Mohsin 采访时还表示，美国永远不会拖欠债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/bessent-says-fannie-freddie-release-depends-on-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:58:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
